{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"67d4cd1df1","title":"七律·洪都","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a5074e8504","index":0,"year":1965,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"67d4cd1df1"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji48","name":"毛泽东全集第48卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/48-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji48":{"comments":[{"id":"ef3e1c1bff","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"祖生击梅，祖生，即东晋名将祖巡。公元304年甸奴族刘渊在黄河流域建立汉国。中原大乱，祖逃率领亲党数百家来投镇守建（今南京市）的晋元帝司马容。313年祖邀要求率兵北代，被任为奋威将军、豫州刺史，率部曲百余家渡江北上，中流击梅，立普收复中原。击辑，敲打船浆，后用以形容有志报国的抱负和气概。"},{"id":"6747d40976","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"闻鸡，这里化用闻鸡起舞的典故。《晋书·祖邀传》：“与司空刘瑶俱为司州主海，情好绸续，共被同。中夜闻荒鸡鸣，现觉日：“此非恶声也。因起舞。祖邀和刘瑶年轻时都有大志，互相勉励振作，因此听到鸡鸣就起床舞剑。后以“闻鸡起舞”比喻有志之士奋起行动。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ada1946ee5","type":"title","text":"七律·洪都","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"ef3e1c1bff","type":"paragraph","text":"到得洪都又一年，","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"6747d40976","type":"paragraph","text":"祖生击梅以至今传。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"352c83079f","type":"paragraph","text":"闻鸡以久听南天雨，","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"466b51899c","type":"paragraph","text":"立马曾挥北地鞭。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"5bc3de57f9","type":"paragraph","text":"雪飞来成废料，","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"af822a6159","type":"paragraph","text":"彩云长在有新天。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"9032687c63","type":"paragraph","text":"年年后浪推前浪，","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"378f6994bc","type":"paragraph","text":"江草江花处处鲜。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"},{"id":"33c900a3b7","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]洪都，旧南昌府的别称。清、唐、宋三代曾以南昌为洪州治所，又为东南都会，因而得名。这里指江西省南昌市。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1"}],"page":{"id":"a19c3f648d","publicationId":"maoquanji48","articleId":"67d4cd1df1","start":280,"end":280}}}},"__N_SSG":true}